{"tid":1803773,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"教育合作 - 古德明","createTime":"2019-12-30T12:46:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T13:03:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"96c441013a26c0d897fb8fdc64f3f8a4fe8e2d3a","tid":1803773,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T12:46:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20191229/20833252/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191229%2F20833252%2F&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkcRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=b3d592a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191229%2F20833252%2F&h=129ff40e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20191229/20833252/</a><br />\n<br />\n教育合作 - 古德明<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191229/large/1577525789_ef2d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191229%2Flarge%2F1577525789_ef2d.jpg&h=52b217db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTwitter（@badiucao）圖片(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n八月杪，澳洲教育部長特漢宣布：「有外國干預澳洲大學事務，大學人員或心懷恐懼，言行自我約束。教育部為此將成立工作小組，防止外國干預，保護學術自由。」中共外交部發言人耿爽馬上反駁說：「中國滲透澳洲大學之說，無非子虛烏有。把教育合作變成政治，對雙方都沒有好處。」他說得大義凜然。<br />\n<br />\n不過，七月二十四日，澳洲昆士蘭大學學生帕夫勞（Drew Pavlou）等集會，支持香港反暴政運動，竟然遭二百多名中共籍留學生包圍打罵，而中共駐布里斯本總領事徐杰讚譽這種「自發愛國行為」之餘，還怒斥帕夫勞是「致力分裂中國的反華分子」，帕夫勞更受到死亡恐嚇。又十二月二日，香港民主派代表黎恩灝、李卓人等赴澳洲國立大學，準備出席研討會，講述香港近月的反暴政運動，大學竟然以「擔心保安」為言，突然取消借用會場許可。然則澳洲教育部長所言，真是「子虛烏有」嗎？<br />\n<br />\n而這些「子虛烏有」故事，當然也見於其他民主國家，例如十一月五日，英國國會外交事務專門委員會發表報告說：「中國政府力圖影響英國大學的課程與研究計劃，同時，孔子學院官員曾沒收學術會議上談六四、臺灣、西藏等的論文，中國大陸學生學者協會則充當政治工具，監視僑居英國的華裔異議者。」然則「把教育合作變成政治」的究竟是誰？ <br />\n<br />\n古德明<br />\n電郵 :appledailykoo@gmail.com"},{"pid":"7b99b1ac0134f12d2a48e87116ded2ac4b6b0aa4","tid":1803773,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T12:46:22.000Z","msg":"德國聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MHkcG1&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkcRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=4fe99549\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2. deadline 30/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/369xL99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F369xL99&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkcRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=141fc508\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/369xL99</a></span><br />\n3. <ins>暫時最後一個</ins> deadline 1/1 <span style=\"color: red;\">仲要32000人 </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">［附教學］ <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1803675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1803675</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkcRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=616f5124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">簽完share條link去tg</span></span>"},{"pid":"e0a079d29b0df48b66f68eb0143b38de6efd83f1","tid":1803773,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-1